title: Placido Domingo - Songs CD (2012) 320k (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Here again is more wonderful music from the greatest Mr. Placido Domingo

This CD is a special find for me personally as it includes one of my most
favourite songs - The love theme from The Godfather movie series done
by Placido in Spanish as it turns out. (Speak Softly love - originally by
Mr. Al Martino)

It also has a gloriously beautiful rendition of the famous French song
Sous le Ciel de Paris (one-time famously done by Edith Piaf)

And Besame Mucho is also one of my most favourite songs too.
There's other great songs such as "From this moment on" and "My heart will go on"
and "I'll be loving you eternally" "What a wonderful world" - see listings below and
nice pdf booklet included

Thanks for seeding

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
